We are a certified mold remediation service designed to remove mold from surfaces and from the air.
Indoor air quality is a growing concern for residential and commercial property owners. Whether you have mold in your bathroom or basement, office or warehouse, Steri Mobile provides safe, effective and inexpensive mold remediation in Montreal and surrounding areas.
